            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Create beautiful, weather-resistant plant markers for your garden using laser-cut wood.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">7 min read</div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Related Article 3 -->
        <article class="card card-hover overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-400 to-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-12 h-12 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 2L2 7V10C2 16 6 20.5 12 22C18 20.5 22 16 22 10V7L12 2Z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">
              <a href="/blog/laser-safety-guide" class="hover:text-primary-500 transition-colors">
                Essential Laser Cutting Safety Guide
              </a>
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
              Stay safe while creating amazing projects. Learn the essential safety practices.
            </p>
            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">6 min read</div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }
  
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    @apply text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-6 mb-3;
  }
  
